=head1 DESCRIPTION

An object representing the payment responsibilities accepted by the
collaboration member for query and job compute costs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> IsResponsible => Bool

Indicates whether the collaboration member has accepted to pay for job
compute costs (C<TRUE>) or has not accepted to pay for query and job
compute costs (C<FALSE>).

There is only one member who pays for queries and jobs.

An error message is returned for the following reasons:

=over

=item *

If you set the value to C<FALSE> but you are responsible to pay for
query and job compute costs.

=item *

If you set the value to C<TRUE> but you are not responsible to pay for
query and job compute costs.

=back




